snippet: Inbee Park shot a four-under-par 68 to take a two-stroke lead after the third round of the HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore ahead of top-ranked Lydia Ko and Stacy Lewis.
abstract: Inbee Parks takes third-round lead at HSBC Women's Champions golf tournament in Singapore.
lead_paragraph: Inbee Park shot a four-under-par 68 to take a two-stroke lead after the third round of the HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore ahead of top-ranked Lydia Ko and Stacy Lewis.
